beer.beer_description:
Our friends at Unseen Creatures Brewing invited us over to brew a style which we both really enjoy drinking, a traditional West Coast IPA. An easy drinking 7 % ABV, primarily C-hops with a touch of Simcoe,  blending sweetness with sticky, resiny bitterness. 

This is our take on the beer that we brewed in the US, brewed in Sweden.

Hops: Chinook, Citra, Columbus, Cascade and Simcoe.
